(1, 1, 1, 'Complete Guide to Explore Coorg', 'Complete Guide to Explore Coorg', 'Now you must be thinking that a trip to Coorg is going to be expensive! Well, that doesn’t need to be true! You can plan a trip to Coorg without putting much pressure on your wallet.', '    <p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">You will get married and begin a brand-new trip with the love of your life! You will obviously wish to begin your wedded life in the most romantic and also impressive means. For that, you will have to select the perfect honeymoon destination! How does a honeymoon bordered by turquoise water, lengthy stretches of white sparkling sand and strings of palm trees sound? Well, you will locate this exotic heaven in the islands of Andaman and also Nicobar. Lots of newly-wedded couples picked Andaman and also Nicobar as their honeymoon destination and also you can too!</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">When you get to the Andaman and also Nicobar Islands with your cherished, you will certainly reach invest a romantic time while seeing the attractive tourist places and participating in the many fun things the islands need to supply! However prior to you take place your honeymoon in Andaman and Nicobar, you will require a best Andaman and also Nicobar honeymoon overview! So, here you go!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g9f55616c3224e2352f4b399656624c15e5cb894d5f22ee686a08c84b8c9ae0690d84b2f105eb5fccf17b059e3e4321be_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"209\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: right; margin: 7px 0px 7px 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Exactly how would certainly you like to awaken to the sights of hazy landscapes, environment-friendly hillsides with stunning falls streaming through and also the smell of fresh coffee? We see the traveller in you are already reaching out for the backpack. Go ahead as well as load your bags, your location awaits you in Coorg or Madikeri! You will have lots of outstanding areas to check out and points to do in Coorg. Really, you remain in for an incredible time!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Now you should be thinking that a trip to Coorg is going to be costly! Well, that does not need to be real! You can prepare a journey to Coorg without putting much pressure on your purse! How? By following this Coorg traveling guide for a spending plan trip!</div></span></p><p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Here is exactly how to get to Coorg.</span></b></div><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The complying with 3 are your options for reaching Coorg. Read on and select the one you locate ideal.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">By air</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coorg doesn\'t have its very own airport terminal. The local airport terminal is 164 km away, in Mangalore. So, you can land in Mangalore and after that take a taxi to Coorg. It will take you around 3 and also a fifty percent hrs to get to.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">By train</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">There is no train station in Coorg. Yet the local one is Mysore which is 95 kilometres away. From there, you will certainly obtain a cab or public transportation for Croog.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">By road</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coorg is well-connected to the adjoining cities like Bengaluru, Mangalore and Mysore through bus solutions. You can likewise drive to capital community.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g921b6604b77158e003fd157720639083cf45755f31da5b4138f756be9078a815da9002dd8a45fd3052601eb1eff00bd5_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: right; margin: 7px 0px 7px 14px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Below are the best locations to see in Coorg</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coorg is such a gorgeous town. So, it\'s quite evident that there are many magnificent places to visit in Coorg As well as the very best component? Several of these areas have no entry charge as well as some charge a really percentage! Let\'s begin then!</div></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g8b6cd3721938c08d4b54cdcc0c6bbf3e6bedc74f4429e1170a8cabc3d78774e6f61d7498edb77cb7b430a72bc95708cb_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"229\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: left; margin: 7px 14px 7px 0px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Abbey Falls</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coorg is house to a lot of captivating falls and also if you do not have a falls or more on your taking in the sights list, it will certainly not be fair. So, let\'s begin your trip with the lovely Abbey Falls It falls from a height of 70 feet and also is a splendid sight. If you intend your journey below in winter season, you will see the most marvelous variation of this falls. The access cost below is just Rs. 15!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Mallalli Falls.</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Not so surprisingly, an additional mesmerising waterfall is on our list! Found at the foothills of Pushpagiri hills, this waterfall is a true gem of Coorg\'s tourism. While the all-natural beauty below will maintain your eyes glued, the sound of the falls moving with rocks will certainly be music to your ear. Another amazing thing about this waterfall is that no entry charge is needed</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Pushpagiri Wildlife Haven</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Next, we have one for the wildlife enthusiasts around! This one of the best places to see in Coorg houses a variety of rare as well as decreasing in numbers bird species. Malabar grey hornbill, grey-breasted laughing yeast infection and Nilgiri flycatcher are to name a few. The animals that you can expect to see below are giant squirrel, spotted deer, brown hand civet and also Oriental elephant. The entry fee? None!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/ga8ae1f8e825e7c5ddaf9a595e3b1b09c502eb3a89f7b8c4a1d34359cfcdc826d333aaba8df6c0fe32a00591ee8b1f5aa_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"206\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: left; margin: 7px 14px 7px 0px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Madikeri Fort</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">This fort standing on the top of Stuart Hills has actually been witness to lots of adjustments in time. From being a mud fort, built by Mudduraja, to re-constructed in its present type by Tipu Sultan as well as in the future, improved by the British! Come, visit this ft (no entrance fee required) and see what interesting stories this fort informs you!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Namdroling Abbey</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">A little time spent in spirituality and commitment is something we might require once in a while. And also when in Coorg, Namdroling Abbey or the Tibetan Golden Holy place is the perfect place for that!. The objective behind this negotiation is to support the training of Buddha. When you come right here, you can discover Buddha\'s teachings, pray or even practice meditation for time. You will not need to provide any entry cost!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Here are the very best things to do in Coorg</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">You can do a great deal of fun things. Yet below are the best points to do in Coorg within a spending plan!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Opt on a coffee vineyard tour</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">This is fairly obvious and also a must-do! There are several coffee ranches spread over acres. From a range, this land covered in rich environment-friendly looks breathtaking. And going on a coffee plantation trip will permit you to see them from up close. You can wander around the vineyards, click photos and taste fresh made coffee!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g9c6a7c12cdb39cca0a96daccaccc2bcfee5d35ed0d973c07989caa77c848997640ab5b68a8720168f07d0f072de705e4_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: left; margin: 7px 14px 7px 0px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Go travelling</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The majestic setups of Coorg hav