(2, 1, 1, 'Explore Bangkok in Under Rs. 25,000', 'Explore Bangkok in Under Rs. 25,000', 'Holidaying in this Thai Metropolis is genuinely an immersive experience with the city\'s ancient stories\' rich in history and also its modern-day glamorous conveniences.', '  <p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Holidaying in this Thai Metropolis is genuinely an immersive experience with the city\'s ancient stories\' rich in history and also its modern-day glamorous conveniences giving you an overall experience on your trip. The wonderful holy places in shimmering gold and the Royal palaces which are a reward to the eyes are some areas you will certainly never forget as soon as you visit them. Below, you can additionally wade through the floating markets on a boat as well as commute in the city on the tuk-tuks while making close friends with the pleasant residents, this is exactly why this city is known as the City of Angels! Choose from numerous Bangkok vacation bundles offers from trip operators to see this remarkable city.</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bangkok is also understood for its scrumptious neighborhood Thai food and the street food stalls readily available throughout the city. The fresh, brilliant and also well balanced flavours of their dishes is like a ruptured of paradise when taken a bite! The buying scenes in this city 