nlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Old Siam plaza is an age-old shopping centre Rattanakosin Island which coincides area as the Grand Royal residence. Right here, you can buy authentic Thai silk as well as qualitative fabrics. You can also grab some tasty Thai typical treats such as pleasant rice cakes here.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>MBK Centre</b></div></span><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Mahbookkrong (MBK) Centreis renowned in Bangkok for shopping where you can negotiate as well as haggle the price of things quite well. There are numerous electronics and garments stores here that you can see. There are also many export shops right here if you are trying to find branded as well as brand-new clothes at practical costs.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g86523dda64cee9b195d501f610172c29eacf40d0ffe0c6c57c2bdc6f1467d50ae3a3ae3214ed23104d73638c61d64747_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"210\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; v