ous spots. This temple is entitled after a Hindu god who is the incarnation of the rays from a rising sunlight. visit this temple at nights to see the sunlight established over the temple that makes the rocks to twinkle like gold and is a stunning view.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g2911e2586f96dee42d7296c8b3d60a8217867702d0c196ed8b8d7ddf546e3e2346090cc9a6fc69631b246cbabb669eec_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"203\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: left; margin: 7px 14px 7px 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Wat Pho</b></div></span><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">When you complete checking out the Grand Royal residence, you can carry on to Wat Pho which is just alongside the palace We highly suggest, you take a tuk-tuk trip from grand palace to Wat Pho. Wat Pho is likewise famously known as the holy place of the reclining Buddha. In this sight, additionally you will be required to wear ideal apparel yet safety and securities aren\'t as strict as what you would certainly run into at the grand palace. There are more than a thousand images of Buddha in t