on Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Tokyo - Mid to late March</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Naha - Mid-January</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Kyoto - End of March</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Nagasaki - End of March,</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Shizuoka - Mid to late March</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Hiroshima - End of March</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Sendai - Start of April</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Osaka - End of March</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Sapporo - End of April and also start of May</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Nagoya - End of March</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Best locations to visit to see cherry blossom in Japan</h2><p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Yoshino</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The neighbourhood of Yoshino carpeted with the blushing blooms of sakura quickly make it one of the top places to visit in Japan for cherry bloom viewing! Ask any kind of local in Japan for the very best cherry blossom location and they will certainly lead you to Yoshino. The cascading cherry bloom flowers throughout the seeing season with a mountainside background is probably the IG post you\'ve been yearning all this moment!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g76e6edd4f6a98fd7c64c12a816697407a51a1555f73a56ba54fbaa042ee703951a77e561da93d031caa3c12363187d47_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"213\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: right; margin: 7px 0px 7px 14px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Maruyama Park</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tokyo might be the funding of modernity in Japan but Kyoto is the sign of Japanese customs. The old town is populated with not simply a few of the finest traveler destinations however likewise the most impressive cherry bloom watching views. Actually, Maruyama Park is the perfect spot for you to choose to experience the elegance of cherry blooms. Outdoor decked right in the main locale of the Park lies the tall shidarezakura weeping cherry tree, which lights up extensive beauty under the moonlight. Checking out the Thinker\'s Course in the park, lined with cherry blooms would certainly be fairly the experience that you seek.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Fuji 5 Lakes</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">With the magnificent backdrop of Mount Fuji and the 5 lakes moving, the whole experience of cherry blossoms is only intensified! Loll in the gurgling onsens while the smooth pink flowers of sakura trees envelop you.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Hirosaki Castle</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The three-storeyed castle in Japan is perfectly surrounded by a daunting moat and also cherry blossom trees on all sides. Obviously, the events that occur at the tree-lined park illuminates the pink-hued magic that you look for to witness in Japan during the cherry blossom season!</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/gd25cad26fccbb6a0942fe8a4772b054d58df781454b9fa876889523430f81e6733f3f89a4705574ace108ff83cbe9871_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"224\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: left; margin: 7px 14px 7px 0px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Ueno Park</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juxtaposed with the high-paced worldwide resources of Japan teems the immaculate gardens as well as waterfront boardwalks where life seems to take a sluggish program. Ueno Park is certainly the perfect place for a great cherry bloom checking out experience. It is the home to cherry bloom festivals, after all. Can\'t anticipate anything much less from the area. Home to more than 1,000 cherry bloom trees, you can feel confident that it would be an enjoyable endeavour to delight in some sticky rice rounds or takoyaki as you gaze through galleries, shrines, ponds and also cherry bloom trees in Ueno Park.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Lake Kawaguchi</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">As the second-largest lakes of Fuji, Lake Kawaguchi is not simply a popular warm spring resort town yet also an incredible place for cherry bloom seeing! The marvelous pink petals turning the place into an instead appealing canvas is a picture you can not drink away. Specifically, when it has the backdrop of the shimmering Lake Kawaguchi! If you are planning to do a Japan excursion throughout the cherry bloom checking out period anyway, why not include this location to your checklist also?</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Enjoy hanami (Japanese word converting to appreciating the charm of cherry bloom during seeing season) as you see the gorgeous country of Japan throughout the cherry blossom period! Of course, take your household along as the experience of such beautiful beauty is ideal enjoyed in the company of your keys! You can thank us later for this.</div></span></p>', 'blogImages/100139_1643618728.jpg', 'blogImages/716338_1643618728.jpg', 'blogImages/352485_1643618728.jpg', 'Japan,Cherry Blossom,Lake Kawaguchi,Hirosaki', 'Bhuvan Gupta	', '2022-01-31 08:45:28', '2022-01-31 08:45:28');
