(12, 2, 6, '5 Reasons to Visit Hong Kong', '5 Reasons to Visit Hong Kong', 'This has undoubtedly made Hong Kong a cultural and business hub of Asia. From trade and commerce to hospitality and tourism.', '  <p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Magnificently built over 200+ islands Hong Kong is a perfect combination of traditional and modern-day society. This has definitely made Hong Kong a cultural and also service hub of Asia. From trade as well as business to friendliness and tourist, Hong Kong has something to use to its every site visitor. Its incredibly lively ambience and also vibrant ambiance makes you really feel active and makes you want to completely take pleasure in every moment of your trip to this simply worldwide location.</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g270ba96640395430e3a866dc5e4e3b407e11ee56b52b80a490dac96790482cde614cb81eb465b6d2e94ef83a75a0083c_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: right; margin: 7px 0px 7px 14px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Enjoying The Best Journey And Also Theme Parks at Disney Land</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The moment one hears about Hong Kong, the renowned Disneyland comes first in mind. There are public transportation such as buses and train shuttles to get to the area which operate at regular periods. At the entry itself, you can take pleasure in clicking photos and also selfies with the prominent Mickey and Minnie Computer mouse as well as different animation characters you matured watching. Room Mountain is the fastest roller rollercoaster flight that takes you worldwide of Star Wars with impressive aesthetic and songs impacts. Additionally, the RC Racer flight thrills as you reach the edge of the tracks as well as begin imagining all the consequences of the flight going wrong. Paint the Evening Parade is an additional highlight where you reach meet all the Disney personalities in neon lights dancing to songs along with the giant crowd. The park is not limited to just Disney characters as you reach ride the Iron Guy experience too. For people who like extra thrilling things, there exists a Mystic Chateau which is referred to as the haunted mansion where all the artefacts come to life frightening you throughout the trip. All in all, this location is a must-visit if you intend a journey to Hong Kong as the above points stated about the park are just beginners on a plate.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Ocean Park</span></b></div></b><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Right here, you can observe the water animals including seals, dolphins, sea jelly and penguins. It is an aquatic park positioned in the Southern Area of Hong Kong. Look at the giant pandas playing on the bamboos as well as engaging with them is happiness. In addition, dolphin live program performances are something to expect it. It does not stop right here as you discover the thrilling rides in the park in addition to a fantastic dining experience surrounded by the aquarium consisting of a selection of water varieties.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/gb4ad6513a8d99a2528f86eab915ee0044967f3c9262a5766fabb59319c1fab7779c6ea6881f036f54ad55f925c75798a_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"213\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: left; margin: 7px 14px 7px 0px;\"><b><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Appreciating One of The Best Sky Lines On The Planet</span></b></div></b><span styl