, a preferred tourist hot spot in Zurich meant for. On visiting this place located at a distance of 0.6 kilometres from the city centre you will get to see some great sights of the Old Town, the Great Minster, and also the Limmat River. It was when a fourth-century ft which has actually currently been converted into a park containing benches, lovely Linden trees, and also gigantic chess collections that can be made use of to play, which is why visiting this destination needs to be consisted of in the list of the most effective points to do in Zurich.</div></span><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So, it is the existence of all these attractive locations stated above which makes Zurich a \'Paradise\' for vacationers as well as for the locals. As a matter of fact, it\'s words \'Exquisite\' that can best be utilized to define this terrific \'Swiss\' city.</div></span></p>', 'blogImages/738949_1643620265.jpg', 'blogImages/36992_1643620265.jpg', 'blogImages/221404_1643620265.jpg', 'Zurich,Lindenhof,Rhine Falls,Chocolate Factory', 'Bhuvan Gupta	', '2022-01-31 09:11:05', '2022-01-31 09:11:05'),
(14, 2, 7, '5 Fun Places to Visit in Rome In 2021', '5 Fun Places to Visit in Rome In 2021', 'Rome in March is a crazy see-saw of cold gusts, the autumn breeze, the occasional shower and the romance of spring. Often called the Eternal City.', ' <p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\">Rome in March is a crazy see-saw of chilly gusts, the fall wind, the occasional shower and also the love of spring. Typically called the Eternal City, Rome in March is as mighty a crowd-puller as ever before. If you\'re in Rome in March, there\'s plenty of areas to see.</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></font></div><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/g3627e96ef0b64d1c2a8cbe81671c19087432b14e07c69b7577cc93132292d66a96e97857814bdc8a7e1b912f7af74188_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"213\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px; float: right; margin: 7px 0px 7px 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">From thousand-year-old monuments to a few of the earliest cobbled roads in the world, Rome is a spectacle for tourists. Prior to visiting Rome in March, try as well as go to during Easter. The whole city turns into one significant event, with parties, cultural activities and also accomplishments held throughout the city.</div></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p><div style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; color: rgb(45, 45, 45);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><br></font></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/gdfaa30f314eac345c43f752b7ea014a713fdf7efc7ac265eb26de54ddf6086416f74a391820f937e64849f2469369ed3_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"213\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; float: right; margin: 7px 0px 7px 14px;\"></span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1rem;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Rome is ideal experienced either on foot or by bike. The city is rather risk-free, so you can amble down the old roads of Rome late right into the night. The temperatures vary between 10 and 15 degrees Celsius, which is a welcome respite from the drenching-hot summertimes in India. The breeze is filled with the aroma of flowers and also the moisture of spring, and all this makes Rome an amazing place to go to in March.</span></div></span></div><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><br></font></div><b style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Sistine Chapel</b></div></b><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">The Sistine Chapel is, without a doubt, among the most humbling visitor attractions worldwide. As you take in the divine masonry, you will certainly notice a divine existence take you by the hand and also stroll you through evictions of what appears like Heaven. The Sistine Church is an experience, nay, it is Rome itself. Definitely, among the most effective locations to check out in Rome in March.</span></div></font><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div><font color=\"#2d2d2d\" face=\"Source Code Pro, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Liberation Mono, Courier New, monospace\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto;\"><img src=\"https://pixabay.com/get/gb7262f19ac572078e46f26c5ce13224a580c8c4afde6cb1575637cb7c0f356d309ef82b76fcff839ebd8f5bdf5105def_640.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"213\" style=\"text-align: justify; box-sizing: inherit; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: top; float: left; margin: 7px 14px 7px 0px;\"></span></font><b style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;