(6, 2, 'Asia', 'Asia', 'Asia is a landmass variously described as part of Eurasia or as Earth\'s largest and most populous continent in its own right, located primarily in the Eastern and Northern Hemispheres.', 'subCatImages/168385_1643604991.jfif', '2022-01-31 04:56:31'),
